Description: This is a re-listing. The other listing had listing errors that forced me to shut it down. I apologize to the people bidding, but I couldn’t in good faith, continue the sale with errors of my ignorance. I’m new to selling on eBay and when listing an item, Ebay likes to compare to other items being sold. I didn’t know they took so much info from other listings to add to yours, I thought it was just part of their price comparison. Anyway..... I bought this guitar with full intent on learning how to play, but for circumstances beyond my control, I have to sell. I would say the guitar is in 9/10 condition. I had it tuned up with new strings at George’s Music and it’s sat in its case for the past several months, I never even attempted to play it. The case does come with the guitar, I don’t know what to say about the case. It zips closed and will be clean of debris when shipped. It will also some with new shoulder strap, amp wire and picks. Please feel free to message me for extra, or more detailed pictures or any questions. ** The amp in the picture does NOT come with the guitar. It is, at the time of this posting, up for bids in my other listings. If you don’t see it, it’s been sold. **
Title: Schecter Damien Elite Electric Guitar. Excellent Condition, New Strings.
